become such a good cook!

1227
01:42:21,708 --> 01:42:22,810
What have you prepared, child?

1228
01:42:23,076 --> 01:42:26,616
This is.. er..
- This is sweet rice.

1229
01:42:26,680 --> 01:42:27,815
Yes. Sweet rice.

1230
01:42:27,881 --> 01:42:29,250
Sweet rice?
- Yes.

1231
01:42:30,183 --> 01:42:31,586
There was leftover
rice from yesterday.

1232
01:42:32,052 --> 01:42:35,626
l mixed milk and sugar
in it and made this.

1233
01:42:35,689 --> 01:42:38,528
Very good! My child
has become so smart!

1234
01:42:43,196 --> 01:42:44,866
Very good! It's very delicious.

1235
01:42:44,931 --> 01:42:45,999
Thank you Daddy.

1236
01:42:46,066 --> 01:42:48,471
Child, if there is some
more of this sweet rice..

1237
01:42:48,535 --> 01:42:51,139
..pack it for me. l'll
give it to your mother also.

1238
01:42:51,204 --> 01:42:52,640
l'll iust get it. Yes!

1239
01:42:55,141 --> 01:42:56,209
You're back..

1240
01:42:57,110 --> 01:42:59,013
You are back after
meeting your runaway daughter..

1241
01:42:59,079 --> 01:43:00,782
..and simpleton son-in-law.

1242
01:43:01,114 --> 01:43:04,488
Yes. l met them. And l've
seen that Heera is such a..

1243
01:43:04,551 --> 01:43:08,558
..diamond that is not
dependent on any jeweller's test.

1244
01:43:09,489 --> 01:43:11,527
He keeps our Radha
like an apple of his eye!

1245
01:43:11,592 --> 01:43:14,497
He has eloped with her.
So he will show off.

1246
01:43:14,561 --> 01:43:18,100
Even if it's pretence,
our Radha is very happy.

1247
01:43:18,164 --> 01:43:20,936
Enough, enough. Enough of
this praise. Now shut up.

1248
01:43:21,501 --> 01:43:23,939
l have been quiet since
l became your husband.

1249
01:43:25,071 --> 01:43:28,210
Oh yes! Here is sweet
rice cooked by Radha.

1250
01:43:28,709 --> 01:43:32,616
l had it. It is very delicious.
Here, you have it too.

1251
01:43:32,679 --> 01:43:35,851
Take it away! It is not
meant for humans to eat.

1252
01:43:36,617 --> 01:43:39,723
All right. l'll have this too.

1253
01:43:40,554 --> 01:43:43,559
As it is, l'm fed up of having
tasteless food cooked by you.

1254
01:43:43,624 --> 01:43:44,692
What did you say?

1255
01:43:44,758 --> 01:43:47,497
Nothing.
- Enough now. Go upstairs now.

1256
01:43:47,561 --> 01:43:51,034
Yes. - As it is you feel very
sleepy after eating sweet meats.

1257
01:43:51,097 --> 01:43:52,165
Shall l tell you something?

1258
01:43:53,734 --> 01:43:56,138
The man in that house
is a real husband and..

1259
01:43:56,202 --> 01:43:58,005
..the woman is a real wife.

1260
01:44:33,974 --> 01:44:35,042
Here.

1261
01:44:40,880 --> 01:44:41,882
Drink it.

1262
01:44:45,519 --> 01:44:47,990
Did you like Meethi's
(sweet) Meethi (sweet) rice?

1263
01:44:48,555 --> 01:44:49,623
lt's good, isn't it?

1264
01:44:55,996 --> 01:44:59,202
Mona, why are you doing this?
Don't cry. Quiet now.

1265
01:45:00,200 --> 01:45:04,007
How is my child? Is she happy?

1266
01:45:04,204 --> 01:45:06,642
She is very happy. Very happy.

1267
01:45:09,909 --> 01:45:11,012
What happened, Mohan?

1268
01:45:11,077 --> 01:45:12,814
Don't know. Some breakdown.

1269
01:45:12,879 --> 01:45:13,947
Oh no!

1270
01:45:14,014 --> 01:45:15,484
l'll find a mechanic.

1271
01:45:27,160 --> 01:45:28,228
Hello.

1272
01:45:30,096 --> 01:45:32,501
You stay here.. in this village?

1273
01:45:33,567 --> 01:45:36,506
l thought that since you
have deserted your parents for..

1274
01:45:36,570 --> 01:45:39,241
..Heera, you must be
living in a grand bungalow.

1275
01:45:40,106 --> 01:45:41,609
But your condition is..

1276
01:45:43,176 --> 01:45:45,681
After marriage, a
girl's surname changes.

1277
01:45:46,747 --> 01:45:48,650
But in your case, l think
that your fate has changed.

1278
01:45:50,884 --> 01:45:52,454
Now, you must even
have forgotten that..

1279
01:45:52,519 --> 01:45:53,587
..you wanted to be a collector.

1280
01:45:54,555 --> 01:45:57,460
That's good. When
poverty takes it's test..

1281
01:45:57,524 --> 01:46:01,865
..forget collectors, you
fail in even a clerk's training.

1282
01:46:03,597 --> 01:46:06,502
Now you understand,
why l didn't marry Heera?

1283
01:46:07,467 --> 01:46:09,471
Because l didn't want to waste..

1284
01:46:09,536 --> 01:46:11,840
..my life in kitchen
and kids like you!

1285
01:46:15,475 --> 01:46:17,713
Just love is not enough to live.

1286
01:46:18,144 --> 01:46:21,116
Look at me. l rarely
keep my foot on the ground.

1287
01:46:22,115 --> 01:46:24,920
And you want to buy dreams!

1288
01:46:26,152 --> 01:46:27,855
But you don't even have a
fake coin in your hands.

1289
01:46:30,156 --> 01:46:31,959
You are an educated fool!

1290
01:46:42,035 --> 01:46:44,540
What happened? You
Iook very disturbed.

1291
01:46:47,874 --> 01:46:50,512
The one who threw
me out of her life..

1292
01:46:50,577 --> 01:46:52,881
..why doesn't she go
away from my world.

1293
01:46:53,713 --> 01:46:55,984
Why does she return to
prick thorns of taunts near me?

1294
01:46:56,950 --> 01:46:58,152
Are you talking about Gauri?

1295
01:47:00,787 --> 01:47:03,626
Yes. l'm talking about Gauri.
Why does she laugh at you?

1296
01:47:03,690 --> 01:47:08,031
Perhaps she feels happy by
doing it. Let her be happy.

1297
01:47:08,528 --> 01:47:09,631
l don't feel hurt.

1298
01:47:09,963 --> 01:47:14,872
But l do. l am
very hurt. l feel bad.

1299
01:47:19,973 --> 01:47:26,953
Look.. l.. l will
always be like l am.

1300
01:47:28,782 --> 01:47:31,888
lt's true that l'm a
branch of a very big tree.

1301
01:47:33,186 --> 01:47:34,923
But now, l've broken
away from the tree.

1302
01:47:37,924 --> 01:47:39,226
l don't have any future.

1303
01:47:42,629 --> 01:47:45,000
But l wish that you
should fulfil your dream.

1304
01:47:45,064 --> 01:47:47,235
Now, none of my
dreams is mine alone.

1305
01:47:47,968 --> 01:47:51,775
Now everything starts
with you and ends with you.

1306
01:47:51,838 --> 01:47:55,144
Then for me, you start your
studies for being a collector.

1307
01:47:55,509 --> 01:47:56,577
Me!

1308
01:47:56,643 --> 01:47:58,613
l'll work hard day and night.

1309
01:47:58,979 --> 01:48:02,720
l'll even sell myself
and collect money for you.

1310
01:48:04,017 --> 01:48:06,622
As high as you go,
l'll be that tall!

1311
01:48:21,067 --> 01:48:22,269
How come this army man is here?

1312
01:48:23,102 --> 01:48:24,706
He must have come to
collect his 10,OOO rupees.

1313
01:48:25,271 --> 01:48:26,741
lf he sees me here,
he won't spare me.

1314
01:48:27,140 --> 01:48:28,208
l'll hide.

1315
01:48:32,746 --> 01:48:33,814
Who is it?

1316
01:48:34,715 --> 01:48:35,783
ls Dharmendra here?

1317
01:48:36,115 --> 01:48:37,552
He has gone to the
tailor to give his size..

1318
01:48:37,617 --> 01:48:40,155
..for knickers and vest.

1319
01:48:40,987 --> 01:48:41,988
Who are you?

1320
01:48:42,055 --> 01:48:46,163
l'm Dharmendra's
younger sister, Kammo.

1321
01:48:47,126 --> 01:48:48,195
Will you come out?

1322
01:48:49,062 --> 01:48:51,500
Out! No, not at all.
Brother Dharmendra has..

1323
01:48:51,565 --> 01:48:54,069
..forbidden me to come
out before strangers.

1324
01:48:54,501 --> 01:48:56,838
He says men have bad intentions.

1325
01:48:56,903 --> 01:48:59,240
They say something and
mean something else.

1326
01:48:59,506 --> 01:49:00,741
l won't come out.

1327
01:49:01,508 --> 01:49:05,014
Don't fear. l'll say what l mean.

1328
01:49:05,612 --> 01:49:07,949
l am a soldier. l
never lose control.

1329
01:49:08,014 --> 01:49:10,519
No, no. Looking at
pretty girls, even..

1330
01:49:10,584 --> 01:49:12,587
..decent men lose control.

1331
01:49:12,652 --> 01:49:13,755
Brother will return in the evening.

1332
01:49:13,820 --> 01:49:15,790
You can talk to him then.

1333
01:49:15,855 --> 01:49:19,597
All right. l'll come
in the evening. Bye!

1334
01:49:19,659 --> 01:49:20,962
Bye! Bye!

1335
01:49:21,027 --> 01:49:24,567
l think l fooled him. l
won't be here in the evening.

1336
01:49:24,631 --> 01:49:26,200
l'll close the STD booth and go.

1337
01:49:26,266 --> 01:49:27,836
Excuse me..
- Who is it?

1338
01:49:27,901 --> 01:49:31,541
My name is Champa. l
have heard that you..

1339
01:49:31,605 --> 01:49:36,280
..need a young and
beautiful operator.

1340
01:49:36,977 --> 01:49:39,081
Are you both, young and beautiful?

1341
01:49:39,713 --> 01:49:42,485
Coincidentally. The
young boys of Bharatpur see..

1342
01:49:42,549 --> 01:49:46,222
..me in their
dreams and do what all!

1343
01:49:46,920 --> 01:49:50,159
l'm coming out. l'm coming..

1344
01:49:50,690 --> 01:49:52,895
Champa.. Champa.. where are you?

1345
01:49:53,226 --> 01:49:55,029
Here, before you.

1346
01:49:57,097 --> 01:50:01,506
Hey! Do you think that
l'm a fool, an idiot?

1347
01:50:01,768 --> 01:50:04,707
l'm a greater dramatist
then you! Give me the money.

1348
01:50:04,771 --> 01:50:06,741
l don't have it right now. It
was spent on the telephone booth.

1349
01:50:07,608 --> 01:50:10,179
Do something. Come back
on the 35th of this month.

1350
01:50:10,243 --> 01:50:12,514
Ok. If you don't give me
the money till the 35th..

1351
01:50:12,579 --> 01:50:15,250
..l'll destroy all this
and take away the phone.

1352
01:50:15,516 --> 01:50:16,584
Ok.
- Remember..

1353
01:50:16,650 --> 01:50:18,687
Else no one will be worst than me!

1354
01:50:19,820 --> 01:50:22,157
35th. Tell me..

1355
01:50:22,889 --> 01:50:24,692
ln this village, how many
days are there in a month?

1356
01:50:24,758 --> 01:50:27,530
Hey you!
- Why don't you answer my question?

1357
01:50:27,594 --> 01:50:28,662
Not you. The one before you..

1358
01:50:28,728 --> 01:50:31,668
Yes..
- Calling you..

1359
01:50:32,265 --> 01:50:35,070
Not you.
- 35.. - Wait a minute.

1360
01:50:35,135 --> 01:50:36,203
You.. you..

1361
01:50:36,269 --> 01:50:38,039
You..
- 35..

1362
01:50:40,273 --> 01:50:42,143
Yes, you uncle. How is aunt?

1363
01:50:42,909 --> 01:50:44,879
Tell her that l'll come
and meet her on 'Diwali'.

1364
01:50:45,111 --> 01:50:47,483
And if she needs money,
then send me a telegram.

1365
01:50:47,548 --> 01:50:49,150
Hey! My money..
- Just a minute. Just a minute.

1366
01:50:49,215 --> 01:50:51,118
l'll send a money order.

1367
01:50:51,918 --> 01:50:56,627
Give my love to aunt. Ok. Bye! Bye!

1368
01:51:00,861 --> 01:51:02,831
Tell me something.
Why was your uncle so..

1369
01:51:02,896 --> 01:51:04,933
..confused while talking to you?

1370
01:51:05,231 --> 01:51:08,003
Uncle..! What uncle? l
don't even know him.

1371
01:51:08,068 --> 01:51:09,738
l was iust teasing him.

1372
01:51:09,936 --> 01:51:13,510
These people get in to the bus
pushing and quarrelling and..

1373
01:51:13,574 --> 01:51:16,813
..catch the window seat. Then
they sleep away. Lazy bones!

1374
01:51:17,811 --> 01:51:20,516
Now all the way he will be
troubled, he will bang his..

1375
01:51:20,581 --> 01:51:22,518
..head on the window
thinking who am l..

1376
01:51:22,583 --> 01:51:26,189
..where did l meet him, how
am l related to him etc. etc.

1377
01:51:26,687 --> 01:51:29,191
Tell me something. What do
you get by doing such things?

1378
01:51:30,190 --> 01:51:31,258
l have fun.

1379
01:51:31,592 --> 01:51:35,031
Fun! Then when will 35th come?
When will my money come?

1380
01:51:35,095 --> 01:51:36,163
She is here.

1381
01:51:36,530 --> 01:51:38,533
l?
- No. Not you. Her.

1382
01:51:38,599 --> 01:51:39,667
He is calling you.

1383
01:51:39,733 --> 01:51:42,137
Not you sister, him.

1384
01:51:42,202 --> 01:51:44,974
He is calling you.
- No.. Yes. The one behind you.

1385
01:51:45,038 --> 01:51:47,676
Listen.. Iook there.

1386
01:51:47,741 --> 01:51:49,611
Hey! How are you?

1387
01:51:49,676 --> 01:51:52,213
Big Brother! How are you?
How is sister-in-law?

1388
01:51:52,479 --> 01:51:55,083
ls she fine? Tell her to stock oil.

1389
01:51:55,482 --> 01:51:57,786
l'm coming to light
the lamps on Diwali.

1390
01:51:57,851 --> 01:51:59,119
Are you listening?

1391
01:51:59,753 --> 01:52:02,992
We'll watch Rangeela in day,
at night we'll celebrate Diwali.

1392
01:52:03,056 --> 01:52:07,130
We'll have one litre of liquor.
Ok? Bye! Cheerio!

1393
01:52:11,732 --> 01:52:12,800
Was he your brother?

1394
01:52:12,866 --> 01:52:14,936
What brother! He
doesn't have any work.

1395
01:52:15,001 --> 01:52:17,171
He fools people passing there.

1396
01:52:17,237 --> 01:52:18,640
Today l fooled him.

1397
01:52:19,940 --> 01:52:22,010
Shall l tell you something?
Daily you fool people.

1398
01:52:22,075 --> 01:52:23,210
But today he has fooled you.

1399
01:52:23,677 --> 01:52:26,048
What rubbish! He was
my childhood friend.

1400
01:52:26,112 --> 01:52:27,949
We used to study
together in school. Ok?

1401
01:52:28,014 --> 01:52:30,251
Childhood friend? He is as
old as your son might be.

1402
01:52:30,617 --> 01:52:32,520
He failed in one class many times.

1403
01:52:32,586 --> 01:52:33,754
So he didn't grow up. Understand?

1404
01:52:53,039 --> 01:52:54,207
Give me that sack..

1405
01:52:58,578 --> 01:53:04,791
One.. Two.. Three.. Four..

1406
01:53:05,919 --> 01:53:07,722
You told me that
everything is in my hands!

1407
01:53:07,788 --> 01:53:10,225
The owner sits and works
and we lie down and work!

1408
01:53:10,657 --> 01:53:13,596
Do you do this work?
- 7.

1409
01:53:13,660 --> 01:53:14,728
Enough.

1410
01:53:16,229 --> 01:53:17,899
Why did you lie to me?

1411
01:53:18,231 --> 01:53:21,504
Do you think that l will
make you toil in such a way..

1412
01:53:21,568 --> 01:53:24,139
..and become a collector?

1413
01:53:26,673 --> 01:53:28,108
Enough. Forget it.

1414
01:53:30,243 --> 01:53:34,250
Radha, you know
that l am uneducated.

1415
01:53:35,248 --> 01:53:36,985
What else could l
do except this work?

1416
01:53:37,917 --> 01:53:40,255
And then, toiling is
written in our destiny.

1417
01:53:40,620 --> 01:53:43,058
lf a person tries, he
can change his destiny.

1418
01:53:43,690 --> 01:53:46,127
lf you want to do this work,
then buy an old bus.

1419
01:53:46,192 --> 01:53:47,461
You know how to drive it too.

1420
01:53:47,828 --> 01:53:48,963
But where is the money?

1421
01:53:49,563 --> 01:53:51,466
One who doesn't have
money to buy a bus ticket..

1422
01:53:51,532 --> 01:53:52,967
..how can he buy the entire bus?

1423
01:53:53,033 --> 01:53:54,836
Take the money from me.
- No, no.

1424
01:53:54,901 --> 01:53:58,073
Take it as a loan. When
you get enough, return it.

1425
01:53:58,572 --> 01:53:59,640
And if l don't get..

1426
01:54:00,139 --> 01:54:01,476
From childhood l've been
burdened so much with pain..

1427
01:54:01,542 --> 01:54:04,113
..that l don't have the
courage to bear any more burden.

1428
01:54:04,478 --> 01:54:05,546
Look Heera..

1429
01:54:05,979 --> 01:54:07,749
l'm giving you a helping
hand considering you as my own.

1430
01:54:08,482 --> 01:54:11,153
lf you think that l'm your
own then shake hands with me.

1431
01:54:14,621 --> 01:54:17,225
All right then. l
don't need to be here now.

1432
01:54:17,991 --> 01:54:20,529
lf you think l'm an
outsider then l'll go.

1433
01:54:20,594 --> 01:54:21,862
Hey uncle! Stop.

1434
01:54:23,764 --> 01:54:26,068
Uncle is right. He
is not an outsider.

1435
01:54:26,666 --> 01:54:28,504
Borrow money from him and buy a bus.

1436
01:54:28,735 --> 01:54:31,005
We'll return it with interest.
- But Radha..

1437
01:54:31,071 --> 01:54:33,175
No ifs and buts!
Come, let's buy a bus.

1438
01:55:02,736 --> 01:55:04,973
Brothers and.. brothers.

1439
01:55:05,906 --> 01:55:08,978
Till now you have travelled
in buses of Kevada Thakur.

1440
01:55:09,743 --> 01:55:11,646
This bus is neither
deluxe nor luxury.

1441
01:55:12,045 --> 01:55:15,519
But still you will enioy the
ride like an air-conditioned bus.

1442
01:55:15,582 --> 01:55:16,784
Ask me how?

1443
01:55:16,850 --> 01:55:19,488
No one is asking.. Ask!
- How?!

1444
01:55:19,553 --> 01:55:22,492
Because the conductor we
have kept in this bus is..

1445
01:55:22,556 --> 01:55:25,495
..not a he, but a she.
She is a sparkler.

1446
01:55:25,559 --> 01:55:29,900
The sparkler's name is Karishma.

1447
01:55:38,872 --> 01:55:40,241
Haven't your heartbeats stopped!

1448
01:55:40,707 --> 01:55:41,942
Karishma, book the tickets.

1449
01:55:47,648 --> 01:55:48,983
Tell me. Which ticket shall l book?

1450
01:55:49,182 --> 01:55:50,885
What all places can you book me for?

1451
01:55:52,453 --> 01:55:55,959
ldiot! She doesn't cut hair.
She books tickets.

1452
01:55:56,022 --> 01:55:57,759
Ticket! Yes.

1453
01:55:57,824 --> 01:55:59,193
Alibaug.

1454
01:56:00,694 --> 01:56:02,764
Alibaug ticket is iust for 2 rupees.

1455
01:56:05,064 --> 01:56:07,102
What will you do at Alibaug?

1456
01:56:07,167 --> 01:56:09,004
My house is at Alibaug.

1457
01:56:09,068 --> 01:56:10,472
And like everyday,
he will go home and..

1458
01:56:10,537 --> 01:56:11,605
..get bashed by his wife!

1459
01:56:12,839 --> 01:56:15,477
lt's better to enioy
the ride with Karishma.

1460
01:56:15,542 --> 01:56:17,144
Go to Jhumri Talaiyya.
In return from there..

1461
01:56:17,210 --> 01:56:18,613
..get down at Alibaug.
2 rupees for Alibaug..

1462
01:56:18,679 --> 01:56:20,148
